  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "vLLM 队列: 推理中 / 排队中 (1m 平均请求数)",
      "description": "取自 counter 的耗时累积量而非瞬时 gauge。按 Little's law, rate(耗时_sum[1m]) = 该 1 分钟内的平均并发请求数(单位: 个)。\n\n不要改回 vllm:num_requests_running / num_requests_waiting 这两个瞬时 gauge: 上游是每 30s 一批的定时请求、每批只忙 1~3s, 瞬时 gauge 的稀疏采样会系统性漏掉 burst(vllm job 现为 5s 抓取, 有所缓解但仍可能漏 1~3s 的批)。counter 是累积量, 不受采样相位影响。",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "none",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "axisPlacement": "auto"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by(model_name) (rate(vllm:request_inference_time_seconds_sum[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{model_name}} · 推理中(均)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum by(model_name) (rate(vllm:request_queue_time_seconds_sum[1m]))",
