    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "KV cache 占用率 + 绝对量",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 24
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "axisPlacement": "auto"
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byFrameRefID",
              "options": "B"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "unit",
                "value": "bytes"
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.axisPlacement",
                "value": "right"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "avg_over_time(vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc[$__interval])",
          "interval": "1m",
          "legendFormat": "{{model_name}} · kv_cache (均)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "avg_over_time(vllm:kv_cache_usage_perc[$__interval]) * 17.31 * 1024 * 1024 * 1024",
          "interval": "1m",
          "legendFormat": "{{model_name}} · kv_cache 绝对量 (均)"
        }
      ],
      "description": "绝对量 = usage_perc × 17.31GiB(总池大小,取自 vLLM 启动日志 \"Available KV cache memory\";改模型/max-model-len/gpu-memory-utilization 后需同步更新此常数)\n\n注意: 这是瞬时 gauge, 没有 counter 替代物。上游是「每 30s 一批、每批只忙 1~3s」的 burst 流量, 瞬时采样会混叠成尖刺, 因此 vllm job 加密到 5s 抓取, 面板取滑动窗口平均(窗口 = max(1m, 查询 step), 随视图范围自适应)还原占空比 —— 曲线低不代表 burst 峰值低, 判断是否真的空闲请看「vLLM 队列」与「吞吐」两个 counter 面板。"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "GPU 利用率",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 24
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "thresholdsStyle": {
              "mode": "dashed"
            },
            "axisSoftMax": 1.05
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 0.9
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1.0
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {
              "id": "byFrameRefID",
              "options": "B"
            },
            "properties": [
              {
                "id": "custom.lineStyle",
                "value": {
                  "fill": "dash",
                  "dash": [
                    4,
                    4
                  ]
                }
              },
              {
                "id": "custom.fillOpacity",
                "value": 0
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom",
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull",
            "max"
          ]
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "avg_over_time(nvidia_smi_utilization_gpu_ratio[$__interval])",
          "interval": "1m",
          "legendFormat": "util (均)"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "g4-01-prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "max_over_time(nvidia_smi_utilization_gpu_ratio[$__interval])",
          "interval": "1m",
          "legendFormat": "util (峰)"
        }
      ],
      "description": "警戒线:橙 90%、红 100%(利用率上限)\n\nnvidia-smi 的 utilization 是仅覆盖过去 ~1s 的瞬时值, 在「每 30s 一批」的 burst 负载下直接画原始样本会混叠成满屏 0/100 尖刺。因此 gpu job 以 2s 密采, 面板画滑动窗口平均(实线, 真实占空比)与峰值(虚线, burst 是否打满)。窗口 = max(1m, 查询 step), 随视图时间范围自适应, 保证长范围下窗口无缝、峰值线不漏 burst。"
    },
